====================
Description:
====================
Exploring effect of pole-zero time constants on energy resolution.

FWHMvsTau_AllChan.cc saves plots of FWHM vs Tau for each channel in a DS. It also saves a text file of ~chan:optTau:optFWHM for the DS.

TauvsChan.cc For one DS, plots optTau vs chan. Also plots optFWHM vs chan. It uses the OptimalFWHMvsTau_DS#.txt file that FWHMvsTau_AllChan.cc creates. Adds the plot to an "Update" ROOT file. From the ROOT file, one can make TMultiGraphs of DSs
====================
Instructions:
====================
1.) Run FWHMvsTau_AllChan.cc on each DS/STC.
2.) Then run TauvsChan.cc on each DS/STC.
3.) Then run TauvsChan_Uncorrected to make correction-vs-uncorrection plots.
4.) PlotCorrectedVsUncorrected to draw/visualize the correction-vs-uncorrection plots
